{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928480/extras/tItle.png?t=1734969870\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>BOSS Workshop is now recruiting new members!</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Have you ever experienced these frustrations while running dungeons? Even after reading guides, you still don\u2019t fully understand the boss mechanics. Even after running the dungeon multiple times with your team, the tension just won\u2019t go away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you afraid of being called out by the raid leader, worried about slowing down your team\u2019s progress, making it impossible to enjoy the pure fun of RPGs?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or maybe you\u2019re a seasoned Souls-like player who\u2019s grown tired of existing bosses and wants to create your own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By joining the BOSS Workshop, whether you're a newbie or a PVE master, all your needs will be met. Under the leadership of me, the Super Leader, enjoy the thrill of battling various bosses to your heart's content!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Ta-da! The adorable leader makes a grand entrance!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928480/extras/Girl.png?t=1734969870\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Introduction to BOSS Workshop</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As the name suggests, the main activity of the BOSS Workshop is, of course, studying various bosses!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">These bosses are all designed by me, crafted from countless battles across different games and dungeons, featuring classic mechanics refined through hundreds of fights. Once you join our workshop, you can freely use them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928480/extras/BOSS.png?t=1734969870\" />Of course, during your studies, I, as the Super Leader, am not slacking off either~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I\u2019m continuously creating new bosses. Though it\u2019s just me, so the progress might be a bit slow~QWQ.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, please look forward to the upcoming bosses!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Boss DIY</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928480/extras/BossSkill.png?t=1734969870\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During your studies, you can unlock hundreds of boss skills. Wait a minute, have you noticed the special feature of our workshop? That\u2019s right! It\u2019s boss DIY!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine these skills randomly to create your own unique boss! Choose your favorite boss skins, and whether you want to create a super simple, super practical, super complex, or even super funny boss skill set, it\u2019s all up to you!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u><strong>Characters</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2928480/extras/Chars.png?t=1734969870\" />Ahem, as such a cute and thoughtful leader, I certainly wouldn\u2019t prepare just one type of combat character. During your studies, you can also unlock other adorable, charming characters with distinct personalities.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"BOSS Profile 01","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2928480/5ba0f4a74915f778f24b9df9ff95b9835d585844.jpg"},{"name":"BOSS Profile 02","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2928480/10def04bf309cee94c61e0f8e94578b7fa8fdbf4.jpg"},{"name":"BOSS Profile 03","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2928480/070bdc6dd26575b2641a152389d4572b2c0fa5cb.jpg"},{"n